{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"42153b3a6a","title":"对普英像党和八路军的任务的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8d894afe35","index":0,"year":1938,"month":8,"day":24,"articleId":"42153b3a6a"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji12","name":"毛泽东全集第12卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji12.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji12":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"90d5dbe2b9","type":"paragraph","text":"对普英像党和八路军的任务的指示口","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji12","articleId":"42153b3a6a"},{"id":"e82d68ac84","type":"paragraph","text":"1938年8月24日）目前普真豫全区的中心任务，是以最快的速度创造普费豫边区成为坚持抗战的巩固根据地。为此，党和八路军的任务是：建立完全在党领导下的有战斗力的游击兵团和地方游击队，广泛组织不膜离生产的自卫军，争取改造友军：逐步改造政权机关，使之成为抗日民主政权，准备将来召集普宾豫边区政府代表大会：召开全区差千县的群众团体代表会议，动员群众参战，满足人民一些道切要求：大力发展党，建立健全党的领导机关，办学校、训练班，培养干部。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji12","articleId":"42153b3a6a"},{"id":"92f7fe1091","type":"paragraph","text":"毛洛胡","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji12","articleId":"42153b3a6a"},{"id":"9ac2442de8","type":"paragraph","text":"二十四日[1]这是毛泽东和洛甫（张闻天）、胡康（刘少奇）对晋算豫党和八路军的","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji12","articleId":"42153b3a6a"}],"page":{"id":"a91b3447f7","publicationId":"maoquanji12","articleId":"42153b3a6a","start":432,"end":432}}}},"__N_SSG":true}